Nyangati Ward representative, Sammy Maina, condemned the incident and called on the police to get to the bottom of the matter.
Motive of heinous act
"We would like to know the identity of the murderers and the motive of the heinous act," he said.
Kutus Location Chief Nancy Gichuki said investigation had been launched so as to expose and apprehend the killers.
She appealed to area residents to cooperate with the police and volunteer information which may help in unmasking the killers.



